product.name: Bicycle Rear Cargo Rack, Quick Install, 3-in-1 Multi-Functional Bicycle Rack with Basket, Adjustable Bike Rack for Most Bike Models
product.bullet_points:
• 【Confirmation of Accessories】: Bike racks are rich in accessories, please carefully check whether the accessories are complete, if there is lost please contact us in time to replenish
• 【Adjustable Size】: We connect the seat tube and side support bracket size is adjustable, according to your needs to adjust, the weight of the entire bike rack is about 2.2kg, aluminum alloy material, durable and not easily rusted
• 【3-in-1 Design】:The cargo basket has three modes to choose from, single bike rack, rear basket capacity of 25L, bike rack with side guards, you can choose the right mode according to your needs
• 【Use Scene】: Bike back rack you can choose the basket mode, loaded with fruit, school bags, or with pets out of the house; single rack mode, you can tie the back seat bags, helmets; Bike Rack with Side Guard, you can be in the long-distance travel, carrying double pannier bags; can also be used with our complimentary waterproof cover and straps
• 【Not Applicable Models】: The installation of the bicycle basket needs to meet the appropriate installation conditions, the following is the type of bicycle that can not be used, you need to check confidently before purchasing to avoid not being able to use
• 【Reflective parts】: There is a design of installing reflective plate at the end of the bicycle rack, installing the reflective plate, riding in the night can well remind pedestrians of your presence, to ensure your safety
